+# Phase 0192 Test Report — Isolated route pipeline acceptance gate
+
+Status: prepared.
+
+Scope:
+- Reads `isolated_route_pipeline_artifact_audit.json`.
+- Produces `isolated_route_pipeline_acceptance.json`.
